model_explanation: the focus in S1 is on Ellen. That means Sam gave grapes only to Ellen and not to anyone else. Therefore, it is entailed that Sam didn’t give grapes to Tom.
the focus on "APPLES" means Sam only gave apples to Ellen and nothing else (no other fruit). Thus, it is entailed that Sam didn’t give her oranges.
the focus on "GRAPES" means Sam only gave grapes to Rob and did not give him anything else. It says nothing about whom else Sam may have given grapes to, so S2 is independent of S1.
